snippet.title: We Got Compagnie! Short Trailer
snippet.description:
Fight an orchestral company themed boss called Forte "The Strong" as a violinist named Maestro "The Guide," and return the Soli Kingdom to what it once was.

Inspired by the Tuba Archmage Boss Theme Meme from 2020, this game was made as a Capstone for UCI during Fall and Winter Quarter of 2023.

Play Now!
https://zxgnjason.itch.io/we-got-compagnie
